## Swift Package Manager
# Ignore per-package build artifacts and resolved files (local packages are sources, not dependencies)
.build/
Packages/**/.build/
Packages/**/Package.resolved
# Ignore top-level Package.resolved for local packages; keep the app project's resolved file
Package.pins
# The app project's Package.resolved lives inside the xcworkspace shared data and is checked in
# (per Apple guidance for apps with locked dependency trees).
# Exclude the legacy pattern but not the xcworkspace swiftpm folder:
# *.xcodeproj/project.xcworkspace/xcshareddata/swiftpm/ is NOT excluded — we want it tracked.

